text:
Yo Khemu #instagrammerbhaiyya ðŸ¤˜, 
Bhai first time room pr mila tha to laga tha sharif ladka hai lekin tum to player nikle. First year k teri story hamesha yaad rahegi. Sath me kafi mazze kiye chahe wo holi me sath dusre hall jana ho, fest, room pr discussions, birthday tera ya Liquid me treat. Kafi enjoy kiya sath lekin aaj tak samajh nahi aaye ki itna bekar games kaise khel skta hai tu hamesha...
Tu aise hi chaapte raha kr and all the best...ek din century hogi playstore pr tere apps ki. Milte hai bro :)
P.S. Lockdown me ghar k kaand sun kr abhi bhi hassi aati hai ðŸ¤£ jldi move on krle bhai bhala hoga
author: Shashank  Shailabh

Last sem kya mazze aaye ghumne me & wo treats, OAT, night out, morning walks, chawpati, uno me. ðŸ¤˜

text:
Ham first year summer k time Prayas me mile the, then second & third year me kya masst bonding hui, uske baad to sath me hi hasna-rona raha.
yaad hai teri wajah se mai birthday me aaya tha teri setting karwane, wo incident aate hi hassi aa jati hai ðŸ¤£. Khair bharosa rakh aage to kuch ho hi jayega tera ðŸ˜›.
Hall-4 k treat ho ya picnic, holi, diwali, birthday ya annual function ho prayas ka. sab me kafi enjoy kiya.
Tere room pr ek din sath me baith kr 101 padh rahe the, wo incident ka kya kehna. 
Bhai tu bahot hard working hai Prayas aur DNA me, aise hi chaapte raha kr. Ghar aata hu kabhi tere <3
author: Shashank  Shailabh

text:
Sharma ji , kaise ho aap? Tere sath to first year se hu,

Hall-8 mess jana ho ya tere sath wo december wali project, ya Barbeque me salad khane ka. Tera first year k mujra se intern ka RR ya badminton khelna ho, humne sath me kafi courses kiye, cycling trips and many more...
Ab to RR nahi hoga tera ki achi nahi lagi intern, ab Zomato me ja raha and free coupons se salad kha rha ðŸ˜›.  
All the best bhai future k liye. Tere se milna baki reh gaya aur grand party bhi, kabhi milte hai...
P.S. : Lastly yahi bolunga ki body fat bhi kaam hogya, bol de usko xD.
author: Shashank  Shailabh

text:
Kon hi kushagra bolta hai tujhe, KG terese kafi epic memories hai. 2nd year me geetam k room se lekar cycling trips and fourth year k last days take :)
Tera roommate ko lekar RR aur raat ko canteen jana, antaragni me raat ko ghumna and tera reaction jab tujhe weed phookne ko mila tha ðŸ˜›, wo kanjoos birthday party Liquid me ya last days/night out Hall 9/12.

Tu hamare group ka planning and jugaadu banda nikla, kya mast jugad lagaya tha tune Manali k liye. Lifelong memories hai uss trip se. Wo nahi ho pata to kabhi koi trip nahi ho pati. Agli baar Dubai k trip ka jugad lagana train wale uncle se ðŸ˜›.

Tera expressions dekhne wale the chahe jab tu ladai kr rha tha ki dassa ki party nahi dega , tera epic chilana wall climbing, trekking k time ya rappling krte samay.

Tere rappelling k video ka delete hone ka dukh hamesha rahega ðŸ˜¬
Paper aise hi publish krte raho aur oxford k news ka wait karunga xD.
In the end bhai aise chaapte raho and all the best aage k liye(many more papers). Teri (unrealistic) Taj ki party baki hai abhi ðŸ¤£.
author: Shashank  Shailabh

text:
Yo Nikku :)
 First year summer me mile the but tab itni baat ni hui, lekin uske baad sath me kafi courses (till last sem), labs and bakchodi kiye. Campus treats me(obviously teri nahi thi koi bhi) and teri never ending sad stories ki intern sahi nahi lagi and etc etc...
Antaragni me kafi mazze kiye,  OAT me Kaustav k sath.
Thoda chill raha kar aur enjoy kr, sare time intern hi nahi krna chahiye ðŸ˜›; ab to quant researcher bhi ho gye ðŸ™Œ. 
Akhir me yahi bolunga, tu kafi jolly and hard working hai aur hadd kanjoos bhi, aise hi chaapte raha kr and all the best for the journey ahead...
P.S. -  Apni choices sahi kr ðŸ¤£, soch kr hi hassi aati hai. Itni treats hai baki ki ab count hi nahi yaad xD.
author: Shashank  Shailabh

text:
First year me shayad hi hui baat lekin summer k baad kya mast baate hone laga, chahe eso207 ho ya batti k labs/courses, kafi help ki tumne. Tere sath labs me mazze aaye, kya mast fraud krte tha maiðŸ¤£. 
Tere se lab report leta tha hamesha.
Yaad hai tere trip k experience sun sun kr hi mujhe bhi trip pr jane ki motivation mila tha.
Tu one of the coolest, modest people me se ek hai jisse mai IITK me mila. Thanks bhai milne k liye and all the best aise hi mazze mazze me chaapte raha karo. Milta hai kabhi :))
author: Shashank  Shailabh

Raat k wo long walks and discussion on electrical kyu nahi acha ðŸ˜›(ofc acha hai) miss karunga and treat bhi pending hai. At last tum kafi down to earth and motivated towards your career hoâ€¦.
